    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a machine that doesn't just transport you, but transcends time itself. This is a rare opportunity to possess a true automotive masterpiece, a rolling sculpture that commands every eye on the boulevard. Draped in a finish that glows with the depth of a midnight sea, this car feels less like a vehicle and more like a legacy passed down through generations of careful curation. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of artisan craftsmanship, where the scent of rich materials and the tactile click of every switch tell a story of uncompromising elegance. The engine doesn't merely run; it breathes with a rhythmic, powerful grace, promising a symphony of motion that turns every mundane commute into a grand tour. This is more than a purchase; it is an inheritance of soul and style.",
      "price": 43500.0,
